62,"uid":34870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>暴雪英霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜香港無咩人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴雪越玩越悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺上呢隻game啲人設係幾有趣<br />\n同埋有ow啲角色<br />\n但係真係好難上手<br />\n升level唔只係就咁升技<br />\n又要睇係咪減cd定加range定有咩special effect<br />\nR仲要二揀一<br />\n新手表示真係冇心機去學"},{"pid":"1e93abb35a9d3e03759f5121534b1bde6200916e","tid":322662,"uid":79735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>暴雪英霸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜香港無咩人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n暴雪越玩越悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n感覺上呢隻game啲人設係幾有趣<br />\n同埋有ow啲角色<br />\n但係真係好難上手<br />\n升level唔只係就咁升技<br />\n又要睇係咪減cd定加range定有咩special effect<br />\nR仲要二揀一<br />\n新手表示真係冇心機去學</blockquote><br />\n易你又話悶 平衡唔好<br />\n多功能 平衡做得好 你地又話難 無心機學<br />\n咁你地想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eeb1692bea81dca2f33754a7edc0354c070482b","tid":322662,"uid":127082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:44:34.000Z","msg":"其實LOL打rank上鑽咪好玩囉<br />\n靠技術，仲要計埋數，預測<br />\n仲要成日更新，有新英，會改版<br />\n<br />\n利申 玩美服"},{"pid":"36891b5cd64abed0d0e6cd648f8b9d2e3cf77333","tid":322662,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T08:54:59.000Z","msg":"中肯講句<br />\n信長最差，啲平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDota 最好<br />\nLol 中間<br />\nSmite 未玩過"},{"pid":"6bee765446e032f34355609fb8bf007e939dcd9b","tid":322662,"uid":3455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blo