0c3ed77","tid":322662,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:24:25.000Z","msg":"LoL 悶撚到 成班on9仔玩咁多年都係同一個map <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06c49411f2f60b3fb7935a4f9ff5d70d2f48f579","tid":322662,"uid":38609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坦白講信長好玩過你十倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係冇account同太多mh<br />\n但齋論遊戲信長贏十條街<br />\n仲未計其他同類型遊戲dota同smite<br />\n畫質、題材同玩法後者兩隻仲多元同有心機<br />\n真係唔明LOL有咩好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係幾好玩<br />\n一開波未夠5分鐘45 又re game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明我地4 對面5 但係對面走場"},{"pid":"81caead6075eca514fccaa257a504db740d0c182","tid":322662,"uid":98570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LoL 悶撚到 成班on9仔玩咁多年都係同一個map <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩moba唔係同一張地圖 有既 暴雪英霸囉 但就因為咁而紅唔起"},{"pid":"bf4a9c8ee61e5d3808dc924bb25ab1110d93e148","tid":322662,"uid":76728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:31:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>lol好玩d<br />\n信長好悶 黎黎去去都係用個幾隻英</blockquote><br />\n你冇玩唔好扮識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩 信長同lol比賽咪又係用死果幾隻英</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLol比賽每季都會調整<br />\n信長場場都出信長（雖然佢係主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n再唔係就森蘭丸、槍神、本多、百地呢啲<br />\n<br />\nLol有時連烏爾加都出到比賽<br />\n但信長比賽幾時有人出過立花女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b9d74d4bfbbfb8e5f28a16616bb08acc95ccca","tid":322662,"uid":55419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"Lol以前真係好玩，但真心講句依家真係垃圾game<br />\n<br />\n依家d英愈出愈戇鳩，愈改愈柒<br />\n一係就秒人一係就坦到打唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以依家都冇咩心機玩落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b54a0558ff9a651ce22f0f1df20f0b9c8b3c626","tid":322662,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:44:38.000Z","msg":"smite真係幾撚正 唯一一隻3d<br />\n真心唔明點解紅唔起"},{"pid":"bfc3bc54916018a7854ce13c27eefee75dded666","tid":322662,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中肯講句<br />\n信長最差，啲平衡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDota 最好<br />\nLol 中間<br />\nSmite 未玩過</blockquote><br />\n認真，信長係班人自發寫，拎隻game同大公司比佢地已經好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼其他冇魔水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n魔水就係信長平衡佢太多硬控嘅機制<br />\n但又平衡唔哂 仲有無視魔免機制<br />\n同時閃戒cd太快<br />\n<br />\n唔獨立寫隻game出黎根本解決唔到呢啲問題"},{"pid":"78e4e5495270bade491b4843f787cce2db11ddc5","tid":322662,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>信長開波岀百地，宇佐秒條友一次，十個有至少五個會走場</blockquote><br />\n你街場咁夾At打好自然會走場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a4f9d4448ef6e78a7f176cf0b63815d739fbe0","tid":322662,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇其他野好玩啊c兄<br />\n<br />\n不過講真信長真係好玩好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暗位 下忍 魔水 好多都係lol冇嘅<br />\n最重要唔會限死曬你一定要玩攻裝or法裝<br />\n唔會定死曬你隻角可以做咩</blockquote><br />\n金川玩魔裝囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲一定係玩魔/ 攻裝先勁<br />\n呢樣嘢lol都一樣<br />\n<br />\n以前都唔鍾意玩lol心諗得無暈技點殺人？<br />\n但玩開先知信長1打5好唔平衡 好無腦"},{"pid":"9041aa7a18cfa049fa32b1b9c60fc73749ed88ec","tid":322662,"uid":107623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>暴雪英霸好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無分亞洲服美服? 邊個排隊易d</blockquote><br />\n無記錯好似分亞服美服同歐服<br />\n亞洲ser通常都係排到韓仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時會排到台仔，香港就比較少</blockquote><br />\n咁都幾大問題<br />\n隻GAME咁team-based, <br />\n但係亞服又溝通唔到, 美服最少都150ping以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有d韓仔用英文都溝通到既<br />\n但有d會以為全隊都韓國人，係咁打韓文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終而家lol壟斷左個市場，由其香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實暴雪好好玩，可惜人太少"},{"pid":"4c4e3013362e37e0b13f3e3103d4cf96d5b24118","tid":322662,"uid":127127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:57:38.000Z","msg":"識玩一定係串台仔"},{"pid":"9af805c5cffa385556a2535872a9739222386c59","tid":322662,"uid":28558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:10:03.000Z","msg":"HOTS好玩呀"},{"pid":"93245d0af79445c8abed347cd073d7e2a11b0620","tid":322662,"uid":89868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"信長沒落，非mh/走場多，弊在更新。<br />\n<br />\n無可否認，mh/走場多都有一定壞影響，但唔會係主因。我玩左kyo都5-6年，敢講依家情況唔會比以前嘅kyo差。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得主要都係班人玩厭左張圖，有更新又唔受，或者個更新真係唔夠好。畢竟整圖班人，唔係以此黎搵食，算業餘。唔計好玩程度，lol比起信長好太多... 更新，系統等等都贏信長太多"},{"pid":"f7b7e85aaab45f4d6249470ea116aad5d6596013","tid":322662,"uid":104499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:31:00.000Z","msg":"信長贏lol十條街  你信長玩得勁轉過黎lol基本都唔會廢得去邊<br />\n<br />\n利申 lol菁英"},{"pid":"2ef2991a8451aa2911b4af01ee4210cad9819a29","tid":322662,"uid":78374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T05:34:21.000Z","msg":"V唔到隱英 走場<br />\n全頻:有ON9 RE"},{"pid":"c275745443913d0ab11f62f109ef28a44f0d86cc","tid":322662,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim